48
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,519
Any chance of some breakfast?

48
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:38,519
有机会吃早餐吗？

49
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:40,839
I can make you a bacon sandwich.
